creator: The Tiny Digital Factory
descriptionHtml:
Manage your team from the pit wall to learn and master the art of racing. Scout sponsors and drivers, invest in your factory to research and build performance parts.

Create technological alliances with other players to trade performance upgrades. Score championship points and climb rankings to move up Leagues.

- No driving skills required, Instruct your drivers from the pit lane
- Collect official racing cars from Porsche, Mercedes, McLaren, Nissan, Audi, Corvette and other top car manufacturers
- Build your team facilities: invest in your factory and research, scout sponsors and drivers
- Score championship points to move up online leagues
- Improve your racing cars performances and drivers stats
- Race sprint, endurance daily and seasonal races
- Chose the tyre strategy
- Race on 16 different race tracks
- Adapt your strategy to the race events

Speed League is free to download and play, however, some in-game items can also be purchased for real money.

Welcome to GT Manager, the ultimate racing manager game for motorsport enthusiasts! Get ready to experience the thrill of managing your own racing team and leading them to victory in the world of endurance racing. With its immersive gameplay, realistic graphics, and addictive challenges, GT Manager offers an unparalleled racing experience right at your fingertips.

🏎️ BUILD YOUR DREAM TEAM
As a talented racing manager, you have the opportunity to assemble a team of skilled drivers, engineers, and mechanics who will help you conquer the world of motorsport. Carefully analyze their stats, strengths, and weaknesses to make the best choices for your team. Hire promising newcomers or sign contracts with seasoned professionals to maximize your chances of success.

🌍 COMPETE IN ENDURANCE RACING
Embark on a thrilling journey across the globe, participating in prestigious endurance racing championships and iconic tracks.. Every race presents a unique challenge that will test your strategic decision-making and racing expertise. Adapt your strategy to different weather conditions, tire wear, and fuel consumption to gain the upper hand over your opponents.

🏆 MANAGE EVERY ASPECT
Take control of all aspects of your team's operations, including car development, sponsorship deals, and financial management. Invest in research and development to enhance your car's performance, improve fuel efficiency, and increase overall reliability. Negotiate sponsorship contracts to secure valuable resources and funding for your team. Make smart financial decisions to keep your team afloat and stay competitive throughout the season.

🚗 UPGRADE AND CUSTOMIZE YOUR CARS
Unlock a wide range of powerful cars from renowned manufacturers and customize them to match your racing style. Upgrade engines, brakes, tires, and aerodynamics to gain a competitive edge on the track. Fine-tune your car's setup to optimize performance and achieve the perfect balance between speed and stability. Show off your team's unique livery design and make a statement on the racing circuit.

📈 STRATEGIZE AND WIN
In GT Manager, racing success is not just about speed and driving skills. The key to victory lies in your ability to devise effective race strategies. Analyze race data, monitor rival teams, and make real-time decisions from the pit wall. Optimize pit stops, adjust tire strategies, and implement tactical overtakes to outsmart your opponents and secure the top spot on the podium.

🌟 BECOME A LEGEND
Prove your worth as a legendary racing manager by conquering the ultimate challenge: the GT Manager World Championship. Compete against the best teams from around the globe and strive to etch your name in motorsport history. As you progress, unlock prestigious racing series, gain recognition from fans, and earn the respect of your peers.

Download GT Manager now and unleash your passion for cars, racing, and strategic management. Take your team to the pinnacle of motorsport and experience the adrenaline rush of endurance racing like never before. Are you ready to become the ultimate GT racing manager?

descriptionHtml:
Create your own motorsport team and learn the art of racing.
Compete head to head online to join the world’s best players
competing in the HYPERCAR category.

COLLECT 30 OFFICIAL GT RACING CARS
Acquire cars from the GT4, GT3, GT2 and GTE categories and take your team to the next level and reach the HYPERCAR category!

COMPETE HEAD TO HEAD ONLINE
Race in sprint and endurance races over 11 different circuits. Enter weekly and daily 24H and 48H endurance series to earn more rewards and boost your team progression.

MASTER RACE STRATEGIES
React quickly to the changing weather and grip conditions to change your tires at the perfect time. Tell your drivers to push when the track is clear ahead, preserve their tires or overtake opponents on track.

UPGRADE YOUR CARS AND REACH THE ELITE LEAGUE
Sign new sponsors to earn more rewards and upgrade your cars. Score championship points and climb rankings to move up to the Elite League to compete with the world’s best players.

GT MANAGER is free to download and play, however, some in-game items can also be purchased for real money.

Developer Website : https://tinydigitalfactory.com/
